These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, sunflower, zinnia
1. the person who growsrose is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who growszinnia is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Flower     | rose     | sunflower    | zinnia    | balloon-flower      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, potato, peach, cauliflower
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
2. the person eating cauliflower is the mexican##1
3. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the person eating potato is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person eating cauliflower and the person eating potato##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person eating peach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Food         | cauliflower | peach   | potato | orange  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, lemon, tomato
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, camping, woodworking, card-games
1. the german is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating tomato##2
2. the argentine is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person eating lemon##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person eating kiwi and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | kiwi   | tomato     | lemon     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Hobby     | card-games      | camping | woodworking | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
4 different games are played: whist, domino, bridge, canasta
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing whist##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the fan of soul is the person playing whist##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| Game         | bridge | whist | canasta | domino   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
City: new-york, paris, venice, edinburgh
1. the japanese is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| City     | paris | new-york        | edinburgh       | venice  |

