.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, old-henry, davidoff, tiparillo
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, hamster, lizard
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the person drinking cola is the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the prince-smoker is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the owner of the lizard is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | prince      | old-henry | davidoff |
| Pet           | hamster   | guinea-pig  | cat     | lizard |

