.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, swimming, water-polo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, house, soul, rock
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the fan of house and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the fan of electronic is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Sport       | swimming   | baseball | surfing | water-polo |
| Music-Genre   | rock | soul      | house    | electronic   |

