.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, hiking, reading
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, daffodil, dahlia
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | baking | hiking      |
| Flower     | poppy   | tulip        | dahlia   | daffodil       |

 